response.overview: April 26th, 2009 :: The Eye of Tyr appears and alters the future for one member of Incoherence! Shark Girl and Sara Del Rey meet in a featured contest. A high-flying trios match caps off a loaded card, as The Future Is Now comes together to face Ophidian, Amasis and Escorpion Egipcio! Matches featured:  1. Shadow Phoenix vs Claudio Castagnoli  2. Cheech & Cloudy vs 2.0 vs Super Smash Brothers vs The UnStable  3. UltraMantis Black vs Create-A-Wrestler  4. The Roughnecks vs Incoherence  5. Shark Girl vs Sara Del Rey  6. Osirian Portal vs The Future is Now  7. Vin Gerard vs Glacier  8. F.I.S.T. & Buck Hawke vs The Colony, Jigsaw & Mike Quackenbush.
